sellerCard.description: Hey there! I'm Ahmad Ashfaq, a passionate web developer. With a knack for turning lines of code into visually stunning and user-friendly websites, I specialize in bringing digital ideas to life. Whether it's building a sleek business platform or a creative portfolio, I'm here to craft engaging online experiences that leave a lasting impression. Let's collaborate and transform your web visions into reality!

description.content:
Are you looking to get a responsive wordpress website or redesign website or blog website?


I am a wordpress developer with more than 7 years having experience in building different type of wordpress sites. 


What I offer


  • Professional and Eye-catching wordpress Design
  • Fully Responsive design
  • Speed, Security and SEO optimized
  • Stock Images
  • Optimized image slider, Popup and CTAs for high-conversion
  • Social Media Platforms integration
  • Easy to edit Page Builder
  • Newsletter Signup
  • WordPress Security
  • Live Chat
  • Email Marketing Platforms connection (Mailchimp, Aweber etc)
  • Social Media Platforms integration


Why Me?


  • Highly Experienced
  • Excellent Communication
  • 24/7 Available
  • Ongoing Support


Whether you need a blog web-site, a real estate website, an ecommerce wordpress web-site, landing page, woocommerce web-site. amazon affiliate website or any other type of wordpress-based site, I've got you covered.


Please contact me before placing the order!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will all pages be responsive and mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, All the pages are super responsive, mobile-friendly, and support all devices and browsers.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer customer support after the delivery?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we offer help for 30 days as well as guide you on how to fix some simple WordPress issues.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I edit my website afterward?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I'll use Elementor PRO or other page builders which are both really easy to use. So you won't have any issues while editing.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Did you fix a small issue or error?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we do fix errors or issues related to WooCommerce and WordPress.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I already have a WordPress website. Can you add eCommerce functionality to it?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can add eCommerce functionality to your existing WordPress website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide an SSL as part of the project
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If your hosting provides an SSL then it's good otherwise we can customize the chosen package and add SSL integration in it.

reviews.comment: I recently worked with Ahmad A. on a website redesign, and I’m overall very happy with the outcome. Ahmad was professional, responsive, and patient throughout the process, happily accommodating as many edits as I needed along the way. While certain design aspects initially didn’t meet my expectations, Ahmad was receptive to feedback and worked diligently to make the necessary changes once I provided clear communication and detailed instructions. The final result is a site I’m proud of, and I’d definitely recommend Ahmad to others. I’d also be happy to work with him again in the future!

Ahmad is a pleasure to work with. He is courteous, professional and takes the time to make sure that all the details were right. After the job was finished he continued to check to make sure everything was working properly. We have used him in the past and will continue to do.

Ahmad A truly EXCELLED in delivering a high-quality WEBSITE DEVELOPMENT project. His attention to detail and thorough documentation went beyond my expectations, and his responsiveness and politeness made the process incredibly smooth. I couldn't have asked for a better experience! 👍

I like working Ahmad, because of his professionalism we are able to work through any problems, also he is very polite and will work very hard to make sure all timelines are met and honoured. It's a year later and I will continue to use him.  I will recommend him to anyone that needs his services.
Ahmad is a pleasure to work with. He went above and beyond to help us get our revisions up and running. He is courteous and professional. We will continue to use him
